 Those unable to fit inside Adriaanse Community Centre in Clarke s Estate Elsies River gathered outside. They included dozens of motorcyclists from across Cape Town.Courtney s body arrived in a white casket after leaving the family home in Pluto Road. Her family including mother Juanita Pieters father Aaron Adonis and brother Adrian were dressed in white black and pink.The three-year-old was found in a shallow grave next to unused railroad tracks in Epping a week ago. She had been missing for a week. Mourning throng turns out for funeral of murdered Courtney Mortimer Saunders 40 who lived in the Pieters family home appeared in Goodwood Magistrate s Court on Wednesday charged with murder rape and kidnapping.Western Cape Community Safety MEC Dan Plato was at the funeral. He was also at a memorial service for Courtney held on Thursday the same day President Jacob Zuma visited the Pieters family home.Earlier on Saturday hundreds of people joined a Your child is my child march for peace in memory of Courtney that began at Elsies River High School.After the funeral service Courtney was to be buried at Belhar Cemetery.